<item>
            <title>[PIG-2147] Support nested tags for XMLLoader</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2147</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently xmlloader does not support nested tags with same tag name, ie if i have the below content&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;event&amp;gt;
 &amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;y&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;z&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
 &amp;lt;\relatedEvents&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And I load the above using XMLLoader,&lt;br/&gt;
events = load &apos;input&apos; using org.apache.pig.piggybank.storage.XMLLoader(&apos;event&apos;) as (doc:chararray);&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The output will be,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&amp;lt;event&amp;gt;
 &amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Whereas the desired output is ;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
 &amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;y&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;z&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;
 &amp;lt;\relatedEvents&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
