&lt;p&gt;Review request for pig.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Summary&lt;br/&gt;
-------&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Currently xmlloader does not support nested tags with same tag name, ie if i have the below content&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;y&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;z&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;\relatedEvents&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And I load the above using XMLLoader,&lt;br/&gt;
events = load &apos;input&apos; using org.apache.pig.piggybank.storage.XMLLoader(&apos;event&apos;) as (doc:chararray);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The output will be,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Whereas the desired output is ;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;relatedEvents&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;x&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;y&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;event&amp;gt;z&amp;lt;\event&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &amp;lt;\relatedEvents&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Modified the behaviour of XMLLoader such that it considers the nested tags also. This is implemented by simply counting the number of nesting and decrementing accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;This addresses bug &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2147&quot; title=&quot;Support nested tags for XMLLoader&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2147&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2147&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2147&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2147&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


